{"tid":1306303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英婦環保飲管插眼穿腦亡","createTime":"2019-07-11T06:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T06:26:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dfac20d8efbf4f5e8393048fdfec086a65de9d3e","tid":1306303,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190711/20725776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F20725776&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852xURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=5d4c1230\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F20725776&h=13b04454\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190711/20725776</a><br />\n<br />\n英婦環保飲管插眼穿腦亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190711/large/1562779060_0c76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190711%2Flarge%2F1562779060_0c76.jpg&h=0b312c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者加德納（右）與發現她受重創的同性伴侶曼迪。<br />\n<br />\n近期標榜環保的不銹鋼飲管大行其道，未料在英國卻釀成奪命意外，一名婦人跌倒時遭有蓋杯上飲管插穿左眼球和腦部而死，死因庭警告不銹鋼飲管不宜與有蓋杯同用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不宜與有蓋杯同用<br />\n<br />\n死者是60歲的前騎師加德納（Elena Struthers-Gardner）因傷退休行動不便，去年11月22日晚上在南部多塞特群羅德斯通家中，拿着有蓋玻璃杯子走出廚房時突然昏倒地上，杯子是玻璃瓶造型，附有10吋長不銹鋼飲管。與她結婚4年的同性伴侶曼迪在聲明中說，聽到加德納發出怪聲，遂往察看，發現她趴在走廊上，杯子連飲管完好在地上，到她上前為加德納翻身，才看到飲管另一端插着加德納左眼球和眼簾，即召救護車救助，加德納延至第二天死亡。<br />\n<br />\n案件的死因聆訊周一結束，驗屍官帕勒姆說尿液測試顯示加德納出事時沒受酒精影響，死因是飲管直達腦後頭骨致腦創傷。死因裁判官指若不是與有蓋杯同用，死者跌倒時飲管或會移位避過意外，囑大眾使用不銹鋼飲管時要萬二分小心，勿與有蓋杯同用。加德納親人形容不銹鋼飲管如「致命武器」，對行動不便或滑倒者尤其危險。<br />\n<br />\n美國《今日美國報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n文在寅斥日損南韓經濟<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n巴布亞新畿內亞槍戰24死"},{"pid":"0a4dd472dc0a8c6c42567f8067c38e581e02599d","tid":1306303,"uid":82935,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"環保撚 殺人+ 1"},{"pid":"cd364fd03b2bae63f8453c0a0dc14c4e4253dbd5","tid":1306303,"uid":186844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:09:29.000Z","msg":"環保撚召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d62d62d7304cca6cf42e1d9f67a29131c0e997","tid":1306303,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:18:45.000Z","msg":"插穿埋海龜個屎眼"},{"pid":"9501f3addbf1622a13f3b0f7c3c2c4f0bf49bb28","tid":1306303,"uid":116547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e72af640687975486073cbddceb1c7dd9c9527d","tid":1306303,"uid":5026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88d62d62d7304cca6cf42e1d9f67a29131c0e997","tid":1306303,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:18:45.000Z","msg":"插穿埋海龜個屎眼"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"人命值錢定海龜值錢？"},{"pid":"2fa21019c723b517e37ab8331433e42e3f356fd8","tid":1306303,"uid":40272,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8e72af640687975486073cbddceb1c7dd9c9527d","tid":1306303,"uid":5026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88d62d62d7304cca6cf42e1d9f67a29131c0e997","tid":1306303,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:18:45.000Z","msg":"插穿埋海龜個屎眼"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"人命值錢定海龜值錢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"海龜"},{"pid":"cf58e6729c8ec10ad1504d2c44f6412f862397df","tid":1306303,"uid":223360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"筷子更加危險？"},{"pid":"b45ddb8ff282533c088a06590e80a3ddd7d2fcf3","tid":1306303,"uid":79056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"源頭減廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae2c6adf402a138b402fb88a401abd1752f3f31","tid":1306303,"uid":109573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e72af640687975486073cbddceb1c7dd9c9527d","tid":1306303,"uid":5026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88d62d62d7304cca6cf42e1d9f67a29131c0e997","tid":1306303,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:18:45.000Z","msg":"插穿埋海龜個屎眼"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"人命值錢定海龜值錢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"環保燃logic : 值唔值錢我唔理，我地只關注海龜"},{"pid":"ea9f3855584250918953783ae9719703acb83b69","tid":1306303,"uid":94739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:26:18.000Z","msg":"海龜無死咪得"}]}